---

<CategoryPage
  category="Quick"
  categorySlug="quick"
  title="Quick Browser Games — Play in 5 Minutes or Less | Weekly Arcade"
  metaDescription="Play quick browser games perfect for short breaks. 2-5 minute sessions, no downloads, instant loading. Puzzle, arcade, and card games you can play at work or on the go."
  keywords="quick browser games, games to play at work, 5 minute games, short browser games, quick online games, instant play games, games for short breaks, fast browser games"
  h1="Quick Browser Games"
  introText="Need a <strong>quick game break</strong>? These browser games are designed for 2&ndash;5 minute sessions — perfect for short breaks at work, waiting rooms, or commutes. Every game loads instantly with no downloads and no signup."
  seoHeading="Quick Games for Short Breaks"
  seoText="Every game in this collection is designed for fast, satisfying sessions under 5 minutes. Research from the Entertainment Software Association shows that 65% of gamers play to relax during short breaks. These games feature one-tap controls, instant loading under 1 second (average game size: 50KB), and natural stopping points so you can jump back to what you were doing. All games run at 60fps and work on any device from 320px phones to desktop monitors."
  seoBullets={[
    '<strong>2-minute puzzles</strong> — Solve today\'s <a href="/games/wordle/">Wordle</a> in 6 guesses or fewer',
    '<strong>3-minute arcade</strong> — Stack blocks for a high score in <a href="/games/stack-tower/">Stack Tower</a>',
    '<strong>5-minute card games</strong> — Play a quick round of <a href="/games/solitaire-roguelite/">Solitaire Roguelite</a> with Joker powers',
